{title: Birth Of The Blues}
{artist: McGuire Sisters}
{composer: unknown}

[G]They heard the breeze in the [D7]trees
Singing [G]weird melo[C]dies
And they [D7]made that the start of the [G]blues
And from a jail came the [D7]wail
